---
layout: base
title: Projects
description: Selected research and engineering projects in cybersecurity, applied AI, energy data, and systems programming.
priority: 0.9
changefreq: monthly
---

<section class="container-wide pt-12 sm:pt-16 lg:pt-20 pb-10">
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <p class="eyebrow-blood">Projects</p>
    <h1 class="display-1 mt-5 text-ink-900 dark:text-bone-50 text-balance">Selected work.</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 font-sans text-xl text-ink-700 dark:text-bone-200 leading-relaxed">
      Research-grade systems and tooling spanning cybersecurity, AI agents, energy data, brain-computer interfaces, and low-level systems programming. Each entry breaks down the problem, approach, and result.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="container-wide section-tight">
  <ol class="border-t-2 border-ink-900 dark:border-bone-100">
    {% for project in projects.all %}
    <article class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 py-10 border-b-2 border-ink-900 dark:border-bone-100">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <span class="font-display font-bold text-5xl text-blood-700 dark:text-blood-400 leading-none">{{ loop.index | pad }}</span>
        {% if project.period %}<p class="mt-3 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-ink-500 dark:text-bone-300">{{ project.period }}</p>{% endif %}
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-7 md:pr-6 md:border-r-2 md:border-ink-900 dark:md:border-bone-100">
        <h3 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl leading-tight text-ink-900 dark:text-bone-50">{{ project.title }}</h3>
        {% if project.subtitle %}<p class="mt-2 font-sans text-ink-500 dark:text-bone-300">{{ project.subtitle }}</p>{% endif %}

        <div class="mt-6 space-y-3 font-sans text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-relaxed text-ink-700 dark:text-bone-200">
          <p><span class="font-display font-semibold text-ink-900 dark:text-bone-50 mr-1">Problem.</span>{{ project.problem }}</p>
          <p><span class="font-display font-semibold text-ink-900 dark:text-bone-50 mr-1">Approach.</span>{{ project.solution }}</p>
          <p><span class="font-display font-semibold text-ink-900 dark:text-bone-50 mr-1">Result.</span>{{ project.outcome }}</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        {% if project.tech %}
        <p class="eyebrow mb-2">Stack</p>
        <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
          {% for t in project.tech %}<li class="tag">{{ t }}</li>{% endfor %}
        </ul>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="mt-6">
          <p class="eyebrow mb-2">Links</p>
          <ul class="space-y-1.5 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em]">
            {% if project.sourceLink %}<li><a href="{{ project.sourceLink }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="no-underline hover:underline">→ Source</a></li>{% endif %}
            {% if project.visitSiteLink %}<li><a href="{{ project.visitSiteLink }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="no-underline hover:underline">→ Live site</a></li>{% endif %}
            {% if project.demoLink %}<li><a href="{{ project.demoLink }}" class="no-underline hover:underline">→ Embedded demo</a></li>{% endif %}
            {% if project.publicationLink %}<li><a href="{{ project.publicationLink }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="no-underline hover:underline">→ Paper</a></li>{% endif %}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </ol>

  <div class="text-center pt-12">
    <h2 class="display-3 text-ink-900 dark:text-bone-50">Looking for collaboration?</h2>
    <div class="mt-7 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn-solid">→ Contact</a>
      <a href="{{ metadata.social.github }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-ghost">↗ GitHub</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
